I don't suspect they could hold off 30 Planar mobs at once.  They key would be to not let the 30 mobs get on the group.
<br />

<br />
I took 9 solo trips to Fear to get my Epic piece, and even went up with another Bard to help her duo it.
<br />

<br />
Hmmmm, if you drag the mobs up to the NW corner, I am not sure why they would leave you and head to the people that just zoned in.  That's a pretty fair distance.  I do know, if Fear mobs only have social aggro, it's very easy to get too close to the Bard swarm and they will trade targets.  That should be easy to handle though, simply stick a couple DoT pulses on the mobs in your train and I suspect they won't forget about you.
<br />

<br />
If push comes to shove, just zone in, solo the mobs around the zin by chant kiting them and then have the group zone in.</span></td>
